  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/996830/extras/f18c37f5964c0550c38c2229df1b72ef.avif?t=1643379498\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br><br>To be a simple city resident is easy, but to create a mafia clan, to consolidate its influence and keep it is not. Your goal is to take control of all points (trade, slot machines, brothels, etc.) and become the mayor of the city. Accurately allocate forces and resources to stay on top! Who can impede you be the coolest? Your competitors are other clans and national groups. Do not let them become stronger than you! The police are not on your side? <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/996830/extras/b5db6b215e2db8faba63b3dd895a8eee.avif?t=1643379498\" width=600 height=340 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Various missions;<br></li><li>Great opportunities for conducting shadow business and money laundering;<br></li><li>A lot of tricks and situations on which your credibility and money depend.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/996830/extras/f16837c5231c14197255b0ec51b3e871.avif?t=1643379498\" width=600 height=340 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/996830/extras/f18c37f5964c0550c38c2229df1b72ef.avif?t=1643379498\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br><br>To be a simple city resident is easy, but to create a mafia clan, to consolidate its influence and keep it is not. Your goal is to take control of all points (trade, slot machines, brothels, etc.) and become the mayor of the city. Accurately allocate forces and resources to stay on top! Who can impede you be the coolest? Your competitors are other clans and national groups. Do not let them become stronger than you! The police are not on your side? <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/996830/extras/b5db6b215e2db8faba63b3dd895a8eee.avif?t=1643379498\" width=600 height=340 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Various missions;<br></li><li>Great opportunities for conducting shadow business and money laundering;<br></li><li>A lot of tricks and situations on which your credibility and money depend.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/996830/extras/f16837c5231c14197255b0ec51b3e871.avif?t=1643379498\" width=600 height=340 /></span>",
